<li class='cover' id='bookCover_50548165'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50548165-the-secret-life-of-groceries"><img alt="The Secret Life of Groceries: The Dark Miracle of the American Supermarket" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1591636711l/50548165._SX98_.jpg" />
