<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer1380129858410662329">The author of <em>Tomatoland</em> and <em>Pig Tales</em> and a three-time James Beard Award winner, <strong>Barry Estabrook</strong> is a former contributing editor at <em>Gourmet</em>. He blogs at politicsoftheplate.com and lives in Vermont.</span>

</div>
